I am a person with the ability to lead and work in a team, a lover of programming, technology and always ready to face new challenges with passion.

I have extensive knowledge in contact center technologies such as Genesys (composer, orchestrator, IRD, Genesys administrator) and Avaya (orchestrator, voice portal, site administrator).
